        "subject": "LU-3354 kernel: Kernel update [RHEL6.4 2.6.32-358.6.2.el6]",
        "message": "LU-3354 kernel: Kernel update [RHEL6.4 2.6.32-358.6.2.el6]\n\n--update RHEL6.4 kernel to 2.6.32-358.6.2.el6.\n--pulling upstream ipoib patch to fix o2ib crash(LU-2967).\n--combine LU-1812 ext4_free_blocks() has changed slightly.\n--ext_pblock renamed to ext4_ext_pblock(LU-1812).\n--other changes come from Oleg's patch.\n\nChange-Id: I808c4f462b4aba2fa02108392f5d134aac90e56f\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nSigned-off-by: chas williams - CONTRACTOR <chas@cmf.nrl.navy.mil>\nSigned-off-by: yang sheng <yang.sheng@intel.com>\n"
